posting again here because we still need a :star-struck: VOLUNTEER  :star-struck: !
We need a volunteer engineer to go with us to Capital One in Richmond Mar 24/25/26! Having an engineer in the room during training is hugely helpful, so that the more in-the-weeds questions can get satisfying answers. It’s also great experience to see how our trainings are run/what kinds of questions our customers are asking! If you don’t believe how fun and valuable it can be, just ask @Jonathan Shih, who joined us in Dallas, or @Kerry, who joined us in New Jersey! They still look like this :star-struck:
